extendedInfo.description: Veggie Dog is an action Puzzle game. Player must control the dog to collect all vegetables in the farm and avoiding from farmer's sights. The story is about one little dog caught by scientist to test a mysterious experiment. They changed the poor little dog to become something not familiar to others. It likes to eat vegetable since then and have to get into the farm to steal some veggie during nights.

reviews.comment: This is a cute app - a unique idea and great controls -  Love that you have a pad on the screen rather than having to tilt the screen etc. Have only played about 5 levels really enjoying it so far. Thanku.
